848
01:25:02.080 --> 01:25:06.280
Raquel, xin lỗi vì đã gọi.
Anh chỉ muốn chắc rằng em…


849
01:25:07.000 --> 01:25:08.040
Raquel?

850
01:25:11.920 --> 01:25:12.920
Raquel?

851
01:25:18.960 --> 01:25:20.240
